metadata.title: The Post, December 11, 1937
metadata.description: Front page of The Post newspaper published in Cincinnati on December 11, 1937.
metadata.text_reading:
Tosses His Dime The Post VOL. 114. NO. 141. U. S. WEATHER FORECAST: Fair, slightly warmer tonight. CINCINNATI, SATURDAY, DEC. 11, 1937. Matter Jan, 15, 1881, HAMILTON BUTLER COUNTY NEWS | PAGE 9 | The Post has dispatches of the United Press, greatest world-wide news-gathering | association. Two States Included In New Archdiocese 
Kentucky and Tennessee to Form New Province, With See at Louisville; Historic changes in the Archdiocese of Cincinnati. Believed Safe. Rights status not determined
